Package: seqtransfairness
Type: Package
Title: Sequential Conditional Transport on Probabilistic Graphs for Interpretable Counterfactual Fairness
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Fernandes Machado, Agathe and Charpentier, Arthur and Gallic, Ewen
Maintainer: Agathe Fernandes Machado <fernandes_machado.agathe@courrier.uqam.ca>
Description: This package constructs counterfactuals using a sequential approach
    based on causal graphs and on optimal transport.
